sequenceDiagram
  autonumber
  participant U as USER
  participant F as Vue 前端
  participant G as Gateway
  participant C as mall-cart
  participant O as mall-order
  participant P as mall-product
  participant I as mall-inventory
  participant Pay as mall-pay
  participant MQ as RocketMQ

  U->>F: 浏览商品并加入购物车
  F->>G: POST /api/v1/carts
  G->>C: 透传用户上下文
  U->>F: 提交订单
  F->>G: POST /api/v1/orders
  G->>O: 创建订单
  O->>P: 查询 SKU 与价格
  O->>I: 锁定库存
  O-->>F: 返回 orderNo
  U->>F: 模拟支付
  F->>G: POST /api/v1/pay/create
  G->>Pay: 创建支付流水
  Pay->>MQ: 发布 PAY_RESULT
  MQ->>O: 标记订单已支付
  MQ->>I: 确认扣减库存
  F->>G: GET /api/v1/orders/{orderNo}
  G->>O: 查询订单详情
